3-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205435\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-3.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-jaguar-rescue-center-tours\">Jaguar Rescue Center Tours<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The center offers excellent educational tours every morning (there are two timeslots) where they tell you everything about the animals, their progress, and the mistakes they made and learned from along the way. They had to grow and develop, but nowadays, they are one of the best animal centers in the world. In the afternoon (after the tours), most animals can go out and roam around.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/puerto-viejo-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here are all your hotel options in Puerto Viejo<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2.jpg\" alt=\"Jaguar Rescue Center costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Jaguar Rescue Center costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-76089 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-600x899.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205424\/puerto-viejo-Rescue-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The revenue of your entrance ticket will provide for food for the animals and general costs for the park. Everything else is done by great volunteers from all over the world.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>General Rules<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>On a tour, be aware that you cannot hold or touch any animals &#x2013; especially those in rehab who need to avoid human contact. You are not allowed to take any photos\/selfies with the animals. And, finally, you are not allowed to interact with them. For example, by making sounds to get their attention.<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/74798&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18232323\/puerto-viejo-things-to-do-3.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18232323\/puerto-viejo-things-to-do-3-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18232323\/puerto-viejo-things-to-do-3-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"10 Best Things to do in Puerto Viejo, Costa Rica\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-2-discover-puerto-viejo-by-bicycle\">2. Discover Puerto Viejo by Bicycle&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Take a few steps back from the busy city life and soak up the relaxed atmosphere of this Caribbean town. The most relaxed way to discover the village is by bicycle or electric bike, and that&#x2019;s really the best thing to do in Puerto Viejo. Cruise along the stunning, palm-tree-lined streets and beaches or spot animals on the side of the road like sloths, toucans, or monkies. The roads are brand-new and bike-friendly as the maximum speed for cars is only 50 km\/h.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n<a class=\"block-googlemaps\" title=\"Get our Google Maps Legend\" data-maptype=\"Costa Rica \" href=\"\/shop\/google-maps\/costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            <div class=\"block-googlemaps__container\">\n                <div class=\"block-googlemaps__content\">\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__title\">Our Costa Rica  tips in your Google Maps?<\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__text\">We made it easier for you! All our tips: favourite to do's, restaurants, hikes, secret spots &amp; more in Google Maps!<\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__button\">Shop our Maps <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__notice\" style=\"display:none; font-size:12px; margin-top:15px;\">The map for this destination will be available soon. Thank you for your interest!<\/span>\n                <\/div>\n                <img class=\"block-googlemaps__image lazyload\" tempsrc=\"\/build\/images\/google-maps-banner-image.png\" alt=\"google maps phone\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17173102\/puerto-viejo-town-18-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"art gallery puerto viejo\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"art gallery puerto viejo\" class=\"wp-image-76355 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17173102\/puerto-viejo-town-18-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17173102\/puerto-viejo-town-18-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17173102\/puerto-viejo-town-18-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17173102\/puerto-viejo-town-18-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17173102\/puerto-viejo-town-18-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17173102\/puerto-viejo-town-18-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17173102\/puerto-viejo-town-18-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17173102\/puerto-viejo-town-18-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17173102\/puerto-viejo-town-18-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17173102\/puerto-viejo-town-18-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltin