iv class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Inside the small town of Puerto Viejo, you will find many lovely boutique shops, restaurants, and options to rent (electric) bicycles. The Caribbean vibe is really noticeable with a change in food, the smell of weed (even though it&#x2019;s not legal), and vibrant Rastafarian culture. There&#x2019;s a wonderful vibe at the beach shacks in town just after sunset.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/things-to-do-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best Places to Visit and Things To Do in Costa Rica<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17171308\/puerto-viejo-town-16-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"puerto viejo things to do shopping\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"puerto viejo things to do shopping\" class=\"wp-image-76346 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17171308\/puerto-viejo-town-16-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17171308\/puerto-viejo-town-16-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17171308\/puerto-viejo