thing to do in Puerto Viejo is to visit the nearby Cahuita National Park. It&#x2019;s a protected area containing a stunning rain forest, beach, and coral reef. Walk the easy trail through the park that runs along the beaches and see a lot of wildlife like raccoons, sloths, and monkeys. Make sure to come prepared with water in your refillable bottle because the trail is about 8 kilometers long. (Also read our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/sustainable-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">sustainable travel tips<\/a>) <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4.jpg\" alt=\"sloth costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"241\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sloth costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-76079 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1371px) 100vw, 1371px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4.jpg 1371w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-428x600.jpg 428w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-578x810.jpg 578w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-241x338.jpg 241w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-129x180.jpg 129w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-548x768.jpg 548w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-731x1024.jpg 731w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-771x1080.jpg 771w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-1028x1440.jpg 1028w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-300x420.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-600x840.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205326\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-4.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Getting to the park can be done by car or bus in 20 minutes or by bicycle in 45 minutes. Spend the entire day at the park and have a dip in the sea whenever you like.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The entrance is free, but a donation of 3000 Colones (~ 5 USD) is kindly requested to maintain the park. Please note that this is one of the only free parks in Costa Rica, so donating is essential. A guided hike is a good idea to spot wildlife more easily.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/puerto-viejo-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here are all your hotel options in Puerto Viejo<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-4-manzanillo\">4. Manzanillo&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Manzanillo is a tiny fishing village inside the Gandoca-Manzanillo National Refuge. It is the last town of the Limon province where the road literally doesn&#x2019;t go further. From here, it transforms into a national reserve followed by the border with Panama. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182523\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-3.jpg\" alt=\"black sand beach costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"black sand beach costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-76371 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182523\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-3.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182523\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-3-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182523\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-3-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182523\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-3-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182523\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-3-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182523\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-3-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinour