Manzanillo-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-600x899.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17182458\/puerto-viejo-Manzanillo-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-ara-manzanillo\">Ara Manzanillo<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>On the way to Manzanillo town, make a stop at Ara Manzanillo. It&#x2019;s a breeding project for the Green Macaw, which is typical for the Caribbean side of Costa Rica. On the other hand, the Scarlet Macaw is typical for the Pacific side of the country. Unfortunately, the Green Macaws are very hard to find in the wild, and it&#x2019;s Ara Manzanillo&#x2019;s goal to change this through the breeding program. Just like the Jaguar Rescue Center, this program depends entirely on volunteers.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/puerto-viejo-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here are all your hotel options in Puerto Viejo<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-5-go-on-a-chocolate-experience\">5. Go on a Chocolate Experience&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Puerto Viejo is famous for its cacao as it grows well on the Caribbean side of the country. Join a tour and learn how they grow the cacao, let the beans dry, and eventually make chocolate. Did you know the cacao fruit around the bean is actually really sweet and tasty?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4.jpg\" alt=\"chocolate experience puerto viejo Costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"chocolate experience puerto viejo Costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-76442 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733\/puerto-viejo-chocolate-4-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/18170733