  <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/puerto-viejo-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here are all your hotel options in Puerto Viejo<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205304\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-2.jpg\" alt=\"most beautiful beach costa rica punta uva\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"most beautiful beach costa rica punta uva\" class=\"wp-image-76075 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205304\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205304\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205304\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205304\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205304\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205304\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-2-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205304\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-2-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205304\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-2-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205304\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-2-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205304\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-2-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/1