kina (Costa Rican food, this place is famous!)<\/li><li>The Gustibus (Bakery &#x2013; Cheap and huge portions)<\/li><li>Como en mi Casa &#x2013; Art Cafe (Delicious sandwiches)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8.jpg\" alt=\"best restaurantpuerto viejo costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best restaurantpuerto viejo costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-76236 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16182001\/puerto-viejo-town-8-961x1440.jpg 