group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"hotels\">Where to Stay in Puerto Viejo<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Spend at least 2 nights enjoying all the things to do in Puerto Viejo. If you prefer to have everything close by and don&#x2019;t mind some street noise, look for accommodation in the main town. Alternatively, stay closer to the beaches and nature anywhere near the road between Playa Cocles and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/puerto-viejo-manzanillo\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Manzanillo<\/a>. All the to-do&#x2019;s and restaurants are spread out, so you can&#x2019;t really go wrong as long as you rent a bicycle.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/puerto-viejo-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here are all your hotel options in Puerto Viejo<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"hotels-in-puerto-viejo\">Hotels in Puerto Viejo<\/h3>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/puerto-viejo-le-cameleon\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/19171948\/Shawandha-Lodge-30x20.jpeg\" alt=\"Le Cameleon\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/19171948\/Shawandha-Lodge-450x301.jpeg\">\n 