d\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17171233\/puerto-viejo-town-10.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-by-car\">By Car<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When arriving with a flight at San Jose, it&#x2019;s about 4.5 hours driving by car to Puerto Viejo. It&#x2019;s good to know that there&#x2019;s a brand new well-paved road. Plus, during our visit, the roads were widened to four lanes. Closer to Puerto Viejo, you&#x2019;ll find some potholes in the road, and there&#x2019;s one specific bridge you need to cross very slowly to avoid damage. You do not need a 4&#xD7;4, but a car with some clearance from the ground can be useful to prevent damage.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>There&#x2019;s a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/rent-car-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Costa Rica car rental<\/a> in Puerto Viejo and San Jose (we recommend using <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a> because they work with local car rental companies). More importantly (especially in Costa Rica), insurance is already included in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">the price viewed on their website<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11.jpg\" alt=\"how to get around puerto viejo costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"how to get around puerto viejo costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-76307 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024455\/puerto-viejo-town-11-300